  title: "Nh\u1EADt k\xFD ng\u01B0\u1EDDi l\xEDnh #2"
  category: 1
  content: "M\xECnh nghe \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c t\u1EEB \u0111\u1ED9i tr\u01B0\u1EDFng
    r\u1EB1ng d\u1ECBch b\u1EC7nh xu\u1EA5t ph\xE1t t\u1EEB b\u1EC7nh vi\u1EC7n,
    kh\xF4ng bi\u1EBFt c\xF3 ph\u1EA3i hay kh\xF4ng m\xE0 c\xF4ng nh\u1EADn xung
    quanh khu v\u1EF1c \u0111\xF3 nhi\u1EC1u zombie th\u1EADt. H\xECnh nh\u01B0 trong
    b\u1EC7nh vi\u1EC7n c\xF2n b\u1EC7nh \xE1n, \u0111\u1EC3 khi n\xE0o r\u1EA3nh
    t\xECm xem c\xF2n g\xEC kh\xF4ng."
